      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/587107619_1354718529482344_6951684090692095769_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc3MDg4NjQzNTEyNjQyNTQ2Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM4LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=yEc7MF-tDPAQ7kNvwHVyVZI&amp;_nc_oc=Adqx1UdStCguGfZ1F-O8r344EyTvpWNUtJ-xuSXSHb7xONNRieT4EffSI2jlkOAycUk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6NzJoUaqosFIKz6K2O_dww&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwZePxiJy83MiQhI6j1LxGV-MNW_60PiVer0ctZ9R78yg&amp;oe=69C9A0C9" alt="Instagram billede fra @roisinmurphyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@roisinmurphyofficial</strong></p><p>The last show of an era took place in Dusseldorf on the 30th October. Here’s a little film edited together using your Instagram stories from that night 🖤<br/>
